org.eng.aisp.feature.IFeature

  • Packages that use IFeature 
    Package Description
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.knn
    Provides a framework for classifiers that use nearest neighbor distance metrics.
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.knn.merge
    Implements nearest neighbor algorithms that merge sub-features for training and classification.
    org.eng.aisp.feature
    Defines a framework for features and the operations on them including extractiong and processing.
    org.eng.aisp.feature.extractor
    Defines IFeatureExtractor and support classes.
    org.eng.aisp.feature.extractor.vector
    Defines IFeatureExtractor implementations over vectors of double values.
    org.eng.aisp.feature.io
    Provides support for reading/writing features from/to the file system.
    org.eng.aisp.feature.processor.vector
    Provides implementations of feature processors over vectors of double values.
    org.eng.aisp.util
    Various utilities specific to the sound project code base.
